zone_analyses.Zone A — Ground Level West: Workers are wearing hard hats, safety vests, and steel-toe boots. The area has been cleared of debris and loose materials. Concrete forms are being set up along the western wall. Rebar is visible and appears to be tied according to structural plans. Electrical cords run along the north edge but are neatly routed and secured with cable covers.
zone_analyses.Zone B — Level 3 East Scaffolding: Multiple trades are working simultaneously. Some workers appear to be missing safety vests.
